title: Live updates and chat: Cleveland Indians vs. Minnesota Twins, Game 158
text:
CLEVELAND, Ohio -- Get scoring updates and join beat writer Zack Meisel for a live chat as the Indians and Twins play their series finale Thursday at Progressive Field.
Games 158: Indians (78-79) vs. Twins (82-76).
First pitch: 7:10 pm. ET
TV/radio: SportsTime Ohio, WMMS FM/100.7, WTAM 1100
